data.description: Welcome to your dream home located in the desirable neighborhood of Terra Bella! This beautiful and very well kept home offers everything you could ever want and more. Boasting 4 spacious bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, with a bonus room upstairs, there is plenty of room for the whole family to live comfortably. Step inside and be greeted by 2701 square feet of living space, with new luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the living areas. The gas fireplace in the living room creates a cozy ambiance that is perfect for relaxing after a long day. A stunning kitchen which features refinished cabinets and new quartz countertops with beautiful open cabinets. Escape to the master suite to relax where you will have direct access to the pool, while the en-suite bathroom boasts a spa-like atmosphere with a soaking tub, a separate shower, large master closet and a double vanity with plenty of space to get ready for your day! In addition to the remarkable interior, this property also offers a 3-car garage. Beyond the garage, you'll find a 28x30 shop with spray foam insulation and a convenient lift. The widened driveway provides plenty of space for parking. Enjoy outdoor living at its finest with a sparkling swimming pool, perfect for cooling off on those hot summer days. The updated landscaping adds to the charm and curb appeal of this stunning property. As an added bonus, there are 2 apple trees and 2 peach trees, providing a delicious harvest each year. Safety is paramount, and this home offers a secure safe room in the garage, providing peace of mind during severe weather events. With a sprinkler system in place, maintaining the lush green lawn has never been easier. This truly remarkable home is a rare find and won't be on the market for long. Don't miss your chance to own this piece of paradise! NEW flooring, kitchen cabinets, quartz countertops, pool, shop and widened driveway have been put into this home. *aerial boundary photos are estimated
